			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Blessed Guardian Arrows if you follow Karana; Mithril Champion Arrows, if you follow Tunare; and maybe a few of the Acrylia/Condensed Arrows as well.  
<br />

<br />
You *should* be able to find them in the bazaar, but I can't guarantee that of course =)
<br />

<br />
As far as I know, there is nothing more 'uber' or no-drop yet.
<br />

<br />
Good luck!<br />_________________<br />Windcaller <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=886614" target="_blank" class="postlink">Staja</a> Stfuplz
<br />
Forest Stalker of Karana
<br />
