			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">There is many arrows you can choose, and many can be bought in bazaar, or made by yourself.
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=66148" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Blessed Guardian Arrow</a>
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=10761" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Shadow Tipped Acrylia Arrow </a>
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=24493" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Blessed Champion Arrow </a>
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=24488" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Mithril Champion Arrow </a> 
<br />

<br />
These are good enough. Remember, just buy one, not worth buying a stack. Only one arrow, you know what Endless Quiver can do!<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1137641" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Girro - Warder of Tunare</a></span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
